init_text: You're Barack Obama. 4 years into your retirement, you awake to find a letter with no return address on your bedside table. It reads "I hope you've had a chance to relax Barack...but pack your bags and call the number below. It's time to start the real job." Signed simply, "JFK."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I'm not sure if I'm more confused or annoyed.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I'm not sure what to think.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I hang up and go back to the movie.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I pick it up and say, "Look, I'm not interested in whatever you're selling.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I open it and there's a man standing there, dressed in a black suit.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I tell him some nut is at my door and he needs to get him out of here.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I tell him to go get it and come back.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He says, "I'm not here to hurt you, I'm here to help you.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I tell him I'm not interested in his help.
